Introduction
------------

Markdown is an awesome way to input text.  It also allows you to insert code
into your documents:

    /* Sample C code you should NEVER run on your own machine. */
    #include <unistd.h>

    int main()
    {
        while (1) fork();
    }

See?  Wasn't that easy?
